.TH GRAFANA-UTIL-CHANGE-AUDIT 1 "2026-04-03" "grafana-util 0.7.4" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
grafana\-util\-change\-audit \- audit managed Grafana resources against a checksum lock and current live state.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B grafana-util change audit [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
audit managed Grafana resources against a checksum lock and current live state.
.PP
when you need a drift check or want to refresh a lock snapshot.
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
audit managed Grafana resources against a checksum lock and current live state.
.EX
grafana-util change audit --managed-file ./desired.json --live-file ./live.json --write-lock ./sync-lock.json
.EE
.PP
audit managed Grafana resources against a checksum lock and current live state.
.EX
grafana-util change audit --lock-file ./sync-lock.json --fetch-live --profile prod --fail-on-drift --output json
.EE
